%!PS-Adobe-3.0
%%BoundingBox: 24 24 588 768
%%Title: Enscript Output
%%For: Avi Snyder
%%Creator: GNU enscript 1.6.1
%%CreationDate: Wed Feb 14 23:33:36 2018
%%Orientation: Landscape
%%Pages: (atend)
%%DocumentMedia: Letter 612 792 0 () ()
%%DocumentNeededResources: (atend)
